1. How to comment on html tags
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>HTML Comment Example</title>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- This is the main heading of the page -->
    <h1>Welcome to My Web Page</h1>

    <!-- This is a section for a paragraph -->
    <p>This is a paragraph explaining the content of the webpage.</p>

    <!-- This is a list of items -->
    <ul>
        <li>First item</li>
        <li>Second item</li>
        <li>Third item</li>
    </ul>
</body>
</html>


2.How to include abbreviations in html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <title>HTML Abbreviation Example</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Understanding Abbreviations in HTML</h1>
    <p>
        The term <abbr title="Hypertext Markup Language">HTML</abbr> is the standard markup language used to create web pages.
    </p>
    <p>
        Another common term is <abbr title="Cascading Style Sheets">CSS</abbr>, which is used to style web pages.
    </p>
    <p>
        The <abbr title="World Health Organization">WHO</abbr> is an important global health organization.
    </p>
</body>
</html>

3.How to create a hyper link in html

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Hyperlink Example</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Welcome to My Website</h1>
    <p>Click the link below to visit Example.com:</p>
    <!-- This is the hyperlink -->
    <a href="https://www.example.com" target="_blank">Visit Example.com</a>
    <p>Thank you for visiting!</p>
</body>
</html>

4.what is the correct way to write an address in an html document

<!doctype html>
<html>
<head>
<title>example for address tag</title>
</head>
<body>
<h1>contact us</h1>
<address>
jeppiaar institute of technology<br>
no.86 kunnam village<br>
sunguvarchatram,sriperambudur,<br>
chennai-600 028<br>
jitinstitute@gmail.com
</address>
</body>
</html>






































